<plot>In a post communist Eastern European country in 1996 the food prices are outrageous and times are tough. A little girl steals from the jar, containing her poor family's meager savings. Then she buys a bar of chocolate from the neighborhood store... As the story unfolds, the real intentions of the little devil become clear. This is a story about the warm relationship between a little girl and her father despite the difficult conditions they have to live in.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?466454</url></doc>
